To open the mysql-terminal inside the k8s-cluster:
-------------------------------------------------------

step-1:
----------
kubectl get pods

step-2:
----------
kubectl exec -it <pod-name> -- /bin/bash #(it --> internal terminal)

 step-2.1:
 -----------
 2.1.1) It will open the bash terminal
 2.1.2) use "ls" command
 2.1.3) use "cd bin" command
 
step-3:
----------
mysql -h mysql -u <username> -p #(h->host, u->username, p->password)
